OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to father-of-two
OL,4,Ckilled by police car while crossing
OL,5,Croad
OL,7,FThe family of a father-of-two who was
OL,8,Fkilled by a police car in Birmingham
OL,9,Fhave paid tribute to him as a "beloved
OL,10,Fpartner, dad, brother and son".
OL,12,FRodger Bagnall was crossing Yardley
OL,13,FRoad, near where he lived in Acocks
OL,14,FGreen, at 7pm on Wednesday 19 March
OL,15,Fwhen he was hit by a West Midlands
OL,16,FPolice car.
OL,18,FThe 40-year-old was confirmed dead
OL,19,Fwhen paramedics arrived on the scene.
