OL,7,FThe two police officers in the car
OL,8,Fwere responding to reports that a man
OL,9,Fhad been seen nearby carrying knives.
OL,10,FThey were not injured in the crash.
OL,12,F"We are all devastated by Roger's
OL,13,Fdeath."
OL,15,FIn a statement, Mr Bagnall's family
OL,16,Fsaid: "On March 19, we lost a beloved
OL,17,Fpartner, dad, brother and son. We are
OL,18,Fall devastated by Roger's death.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
