OL,7,F"Roger had the biggest heart and loved
OL,8,Fto make everyone smile with his humour
OL,9,Fand wit, we loved him very much and
OL,10,Fwill miss him dearly, but we take
OL,11,Fcomfort in the fact his spirit will
OL,12,Flive on through his children.
OL,14,F"We have been overwhelmed by all the
OL,15,Fkind messages of support we have
OL,16,Freceived and feel proud that Roger
OL,17,Ftouched the lives of so many."
