OL,7,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct, IOPC, which is investigating
OL,9,Fthe crash, says that the police car
OL,10,Fhad its blue lights and sirens on
OL,11,Fbefore the crash.
OL,13,FIOPC director Derrick Campbell said in
OL,14,Fa statement: "Our thoughts are with Mr
OL,15,FBagnall's family and friends and to
OL,16,Fall those affected by his death in
OL,17,Fsuch tragic circumstances.
