OL,7,F"We have met with his family to
OL,8,Fexplain our role, offer support and to
OL,9,Foutline the next steps of our
OL,10,Findependent investigation.
OL,12,F"Those inquiries are progressing and I
OL,13,Fwould like to take this opportunity to
OL,14,Fthank those who came forward with CCTV
OL,15,Ffootage as a result of our media
OL,16,Fappeal. This has proved valuable to
OL,17,Four investigation."
OL,19,F"Urge people not to speculate"
