OL,7,FThe IOPC said Mr Bagnall was not on a
OL,8,Fcrossing or wearing earphones when he
OL,9,Fwas struck.
OL,11,FMr Campbell added: "We would urge
OL,12,Fpeople not to speculate, which can be
OL,13,Funhelpful and cause unnecessary
OL,14,Fdistress.
OL,16,F"Our role is to independently
OL,17,Finvestigate the involvement of police
OL,18,Fin this collision to establish all the
OL,19,Fcircumstances surrounding it.
